These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-1::.
6 different pets are kept: rat, cat, turtle, fish, goat, lizard
The people use 6 different means of transport: trike, car, bike, boat, subway, airplane
1. the person driving the trike is the owner of the rat##1
2. the owner of the fish is the person driving the airplane##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the subway##2
5. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
8. the owner of the lizard is the person driving the bike##1
9. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |     3      |  4   |     5      |    6    |
| Pet         | goat     | turtle | rat | fish | lizard      | cat |
| Transport   | boat | subway  | trike    | airplane | bike | car    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: superhero, drama, western, documentary, martial-arts, thriller
There are 6 different nationalities: turkish, canadian, australian, colombian, malaysian, polish
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the turkish##1
 2. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the turkish##1
 4. the polish is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 5. the person watching western movies is the colombian##1
 6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the australian is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the malaysian is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the malaysian##1
10. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |      5      |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | documentary  | martial-arts | drama   | thriller | western |
| Nationality   | australian | malaysian | canadian    | polish | turkish   | colombian   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: house, gospel, reggae, disco, pop, country
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: skateboarding, swimming, biathlon, sailing, surfing, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
4. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
6. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person who's sport is sailing is the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |    3    |       4       |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | house    | pop | reggae     | gospel         | disco       | country     |
| Sport         | skateboarding | biathlon  | swimming | water-polo | surfing | sailing |

