.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: time-travel, spy, epic, mystery, horror, documentary
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, scooter, roller, helicopter, ship, subway
1. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the roller is the person watching epic movies##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
7. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
9. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | spy     | epic     | mystery | horror | documentary |
| Transport     | subway    | scooter | roller | helicopter  | ship       | bike      |

