.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: zombie, mystery, crime, horror, sports, fantasy
The people use 6 different means of transport: scooter, jet-ski, subway, quad-bike, boat, tram
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person watching crime movies and the person driving the subway##2
 2. the person watching mystery movies is the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 7. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
 8. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
10. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
11. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |     4      |     5      |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | horror | zombie | fantasy    | crime    | mystery |
| Transport     | jet-ski         | scooter       | subway  | quad-bike | boat | tram   |

