.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-7::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  pilot, mechanic, dressmaker, musician, architect, doctor
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: climbing, biathlon, swimming, surfing, soccer, ice-hockey
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the doctor##1
 2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the musician##3
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the doctor##3
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the doctor##1
 6. the architect is on the right of the mechanic##1
 7. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 8. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the pilot is in an even position##4
10. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2       |         3          |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Job     | musician | mechanic     | architect | pilot  | dressmaker     | doctor |
| Sport   | biathlon         | soccer | surfing              | swimming | climbing | ice-hockey |

