.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-8::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, fanta, cola, almond-milk, lemonade
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: ice-hockey, biathlon, parkour, golf, basketball, lacrosse
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an odd position##4
11. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
12. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |    3     |       4       |     5      |      6       |
| Beverage   | coffee | fanta     | soy-milk | lemonade         | almond-milk        | cola       |
| Sport      | parkour       | golf | ice-hockey  | lacrosse | basketball | biathlon |

