1. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
2. the person eating artichoke is between the owner of the pony and the person eating cauliflower##2
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating artichoke##1
4. the person eating carrot is in an even position##4
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
6. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
8. the person eating strawberry is on the far left or far right##3
9. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |    5     |    6     |
| Food   | strawberry | cauliflower | artichoke | carrot | nectarine   | plum |
| Pet    | hamster  | rabbit    | guinea-pig     | pony     | ferret | turtle     |

