 6. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 7. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of folk##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
10. the person drinking cola is on the right of the fan of folk##1
11. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4

