 3. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 4. the person driving the van is between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the scooter##2
 5. the person eating artichoke is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is in an even position##4
 8. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
 9. the person driving the helicopter is the person eating lime##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Food        | artichoke | cauliflower | potato | eggplant      | corn | lime |
| Transport   | jet-ski   | train | roller   | scooter | van    | helicopter |

