.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-20::.
There 6 different types of food: apricot, lettuce, pineapple, avocado, corn, strawberry
The people have 6 different jobs:  engineer, analyst, nurse, dancer, musician, designer
 1. the dancer is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
 2. the person eating corn is in an even position##4
 3. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating corn##1
 4. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the designer##3
 5. the designer is on the right of the dancer##1
 6. the person eating apricot is the musician##1
 7. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4
 8. the nurse is on the far right##1
 9. the engineer is between the person eating corn and the analyst##2
10. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
11. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the designer##3
12. the dancer is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |   3    |   4    |       5        |     6      |
| Food   | apricot    | pineapple      | avocado  | corn  | strawberry           | lettuce  |
| Job    | musician | analyst | engineer | dancer | designer | nurse |

 